item.description:
This short snippet produces a &ldquo;Twitter style&rdquo; time difference, the idea is that it will round to the nearest time unit, and display only the integers on that unit. For example 1 minute ago, 2 weeks ago, 1 year ago&hellip;
You can specify the word you want to appear instead of ago by setting the $ago argument to something else as well.
